Invocation Name: safe diwali tips
des: Diwali is the occasion of joyous celebrations. The delicious food, sparkling fireworks, and diyas i.e. all that this festival of lights is about bring in joy and excitement. One cannot, however, ignore the involved risk that it puts us all to such as fire accidents in the form of burns and injuries. Just keep these things in mind and enjoy the festival.
